.jumbotron
  %h1 Ruby Graph Tutorial
  %p.lead This sample app shows how to use the Microsoft Graph API to access a user's data from Ruby
  - if @user_name
    %h4
      Welcome #{@user_name}!
    %p Use the navigation bar at the top of the page to get started.
  - else
    = link_to "Click here to sign in", "/auth/microsoft_graph_auth", method: :post, class: "btn btn-primary btn-large"

